Purpose:
	This XML Schema (.xsd) definition file defines the basic
	structures, types, units, and various other components
	used by NeXus Definition Language files for declaring
	NeXus application definitions.
	This file does not declare any elements.

Usage:
	All NeXus base classes extend from the NXobject class.

